 Disaster recovery 101: fixing metadata corruption without a backup By:  Paul Randal    Posted on: March 10, 2011 8:11 am  (Check out my online training courses:  SQL Server: Detecting and Correcting Database Corruption  and  SQL Server: Advanced Corruption Recovery Techniques . We can also  help you  with disaster recovery.) 
